name: Praise The Maggot, Forsaketh The Lamb
description:
Teetering on this tightrope with a vacant brain. Blade dulled to the senses; fire perished from the beam. I had to kill you, my insecurity being.
 
Aimless wandering…  ruminating epiphanies… I’d rather bask in memory, but I’m at a loss. Eternally.
